
# Dashboard Quick Links

A lightweight dashboard navigation component for Rock RMS pages.

## Features

* Modern card-style links
* Responsive layout
* Optional Font Awesome icons
* Hover animations
* Rounded corners and subtle shadows
* Easy customization

## Preview

Each link renders as a card with:

* Title
* Optional icon
* Directional arrow
* Hover state

Ideal for:

* Dashboards
* Staff portals
* Team workspaces
* Ministry landing pages

## Installation

1. Add an HTML Content block to your page.
2. Paste the component HTML and CSS.
3. Update the placeholder URLs.
4. Save and publish.

## Customization

### Update Link Destinations

Replace:

```html
href="/dashboard-1"
```

with your destination URL.

### Change Link Labels

Replace:

```html
Dashboard Link
```

with your preferred label.

### Add Icons

Example:

```html
<i class="fa fa-bell"></i>
```

Common icons:

```html
<i class="fa fa-home"></i>
<i class="fa fa-bar-chart"></i>
<i class="fa fa-users"></i>
<i class="fa fa-bell"></i>
<i class="fa fa-flag-o"></i>
```

### Adjust Card Height

```css
min-height: 72px;
```

### Adjust Corner Radius

```css
border-radius: 16px;
```

### Adjust Spacing

```css
gap: 12px;
```

## Dependencies

Optional:

* Font Awesome (for icons)

The component works without Font Awesome if icon elements are removed.

